  "short_description": "Start your journey through the depths of a forgotten jungle temple in Malachite: Temple of the Sun. Match colorful balls, unlock powerful power-ups, and construct your own temple as you progress. Choose between adventure and endless modes, immersing yourself in classic match 3 gameplay!",
