  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast, colorful ball-shooting fun across 45 levels. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make matches and clear combinations of three or more from ball chains in order to progress. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete chapters to collect pieces for the grand temple. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Catch a wide array of magical powerups. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play your way—enjoy a calming experience with the Zen difficulty, or turn up the heat on Challenging!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See how long you can last with Endless Mode! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clear 5 bonus chapters to add structures to your temple! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25 bonus levels in 5 extra chapters.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey through the depths of a lost ancient jungle temple in Malachite: Temple of the Sun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/9f92e9fb65470c2051a17795f3724075.poster.avif?t=1738623012\" width=620 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/9f92e9fb65470c2051a17795f3724075.webm?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/9f92e9fb65470c2051a17795f3724075.mp4?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 50+ levels, each stage offers both Adventure and Endless mode for all players! Match colorful balls, unleash ball power-ups, and experience the excitement of building your own temple as you progress. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/b372a5b56a9f6f3a502708e19ed075d8.poster.avif?t=1738623012\" width=620 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/b372a5b56a9f6f3a502708e19ed075d8.webm?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/b372a5b56a9f6f3a502708e19ed075d8.mp4?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rediscover the classic charm of marble matching games with a modern twist, and get ready for hours of addictive gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/f47397dfccdbd92ecff67f1ba1c74adc.poster.avif?t=1738623012\" width=620 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/f47397dfccdbd92ecff67f1ba1c74adc.webm?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/f47397dfccdbd92ecff67f1ba1c74adc.mp4?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With vibrant visuals and intuitive controls, Malachite: Temple of the Sun is the ultimate nostalgic adventure for players of all ages.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey through the depths of a lost ancient jungle temple in Malachite: Temple of the Sun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/9f92e9fb65470c2051a17795f3724075.poster.avif?t=1738623012\" width=620 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/9f92e9fb65470c2051a17795f3724075.webm?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/9f92e9fb65470c2051a17795f3724075.mp4?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 50+ levels, each stage offers both Adventure and Endless mode for all players! Match colorful balls, unleash ball power-ups, and experience the excitement of building your own temple as you progress. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/b372a5b56a9f6f3a502708e19ed075d8.poster.avif?t=1738623012\" width=620 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/b372a5b56a9f6f3a502708e19ed075d8.webm?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/b372a5b56a9f6f3a502708e19ed075d8.mp4?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rediscover the classic charm of marble matching games with a modern twist, and get ready for hours of addictive gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/f47397dfccdbd92ecff67f1ba1c74adc.poster.avif?t=1738623012\" width=620 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/f47397dfccdbd92ecff67f1ba1c74adc.webm?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702390/extras/f47397dfccdbd92ecff67f1ba1c74adc.mp4?t=1738623012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With vibrant visuals and intuitive controls, Malachite: Temple of the Sun is the ultimate nostalgic adventure for players of all ages.</p>",
